{"title":"New York Philharmonic - Handel’s Messiah at Lincoln Center","seo_title":"New York Philharmonic - Handel’s Messiah at Lincoln Center","seo_description":"New York Philharmonic - Handel’s Messiah at Lincoln Center","date":"12/15/2016 - 12/19/2016","datemeta":"2016/12/15 - 2016/12/19","preview":"<p>When the holiday season descends upon New York, it's not uncommon to hear the instantly recognizable music of Handel&rsquo;s Messiah pouring from concert halls and churches alike.</p>","contents":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: #222222; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">When the holiday season descends upon New York, it&rsquo;s not uncommon to hear the instantly recognizable music of Handel&rsquo;s </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: #222222; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Messiah </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: #222222; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">pouring from concert halls and churches alike. Yet few performances are as world-renowned as those given by the New York Philharmonic at Lincoln Center every year. </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Calibri; color: #222222; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; whit